Simple Bug Reports
Bug #1: Empty Task Name Validation Error Not Displayed
JIRA ID: QTP-001
Severity: Major
Priority: High

Steps to Reproduce:
Go to http://localhost:8080/tasks
Leave task name field empty
Click "Add Task" button
Expected Result:
Error message "Task name is required" should be displayed

Actual Result:
No error message shown, page just refreshes

Root Cause:
Template missing error display logic

Fix Applied:
html
<!-- Add to template -->
<div th:if="${#fields.hasErrors('newTask.name')}" class="alert alert-danger">
    <span th:errors="*{newTask.name}">Name Error</span>
</div>
Bug #2: Selenium Test Timeout Issues
JIRA ID: QTP-002
Severity: Minor
Priority: Medium

Steps to Reproduce:
Run mvn test
TaskManagerSeleniumTest sometimes fails
Expected Result:
Test should pass consistently

Actual Result:
Intermittent failures due to timing

Root Cause:
Missing WebDriverWait in Selenium tests

Fix Applied:
java
// Added explicit wait
WebElement taskInput = wait.until(ExpectedConditions.visibilityOfElementLocated(
    By.xpath("//input[@placeholder='Enter task name']")));
